description: From private parties and corporate events to birthday bashes and backyard gatherings, the original, made to order, taco cart catering service adds a touch of the islands to any situation. Rasta Taco's original recipes are served directly from unique mobile taco carts that will bring compliments from your guests for first class presentation and flavors. With many years of experience in the culinary arts, we customize menus to meet your specific requirements. You’ll find the only thing we won't change is our commitment to your catering needs. After all, it’s your party and your focus should be on your guests, not your catering company.
name: Rasta Taco
